title: Hylo Brown & The Timberliners - 1954-1960 (1992) Bear Family
description:
Hylo Brown & The Timberliners - 1954-1960 (1992) Bear Family CD



1954-60 is a double-disc collection that contains all 46 songs that Hylo Brown & the Timberliners recorded for Capitol Recordings during the late '50s. Many of these tracks feature stellar support from Clarence Tate, Merle Taylor and Dale Potter, and any serious bluegrass fan will find this expensive double-disc set worth the investment. ~ Thom Owens, All Music Guide
